options.content: Ford Sediment Tests (10R140 Components)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))
      ,[partName] [Part]
      ,[reportNum] [Report]
      ,[result] [Results]
FROM [PMDA-Litmus].[dbo].[RecJomesa_SedimentTest]

WHERE DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))
      BETWEEN 
            DATEADD(second, DATEDIFF(second,GETUTCDATE(),Getdate()),$__timeFrom()) 
            AND 
            DATEADD(second, DATEDIFF(second,GETUTCDATE(),Getdate()),$__timeTo())
AND [loc] in ($Location)
AND [partName] in ($PartName)
ORDER BY
     DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))

panels.description:
Table used for download data for all parts or specific parts within a time range. 

1) Select The Part(s) in the top left corner
2) Select The Time Range in the top right corner
3) Click the arrow beside table header
4) Click Inspect > Data > Download CSV

targets.rawSql:
SELECT DISTINCT DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))[Date of Analysis]
      ,[reportNum] [Test No.]
      ,[partName] [Part Name]
      ,[loc] [Sample Location]
      ,[JK] [J-K (>600)]
      ,[FI] [F-I (100-600)]
      ,[HI] [H-I (200-600)]
      ,[FG] [F-G (100-200)]
      ,[DE] [D-E (25-100)]
      ,[CE] [C-E (15-100)]
      ,[weight] [Weight (mg)]
      ,[partWeight] [Weight Per Part (mg)]
      ,[occ] [Occupancy (%)]
      ,[met_len] [Largest Metallic Length (um)]
      ,[met_width] [Largest Metallic Width (um)]
      ,[nonMet_len] [Largest Non-Metallic Length (um)]
      ,[nonMet_wid] [Largest Non-Metallic Width (um)]
      ,[fiber_len] [Largest Fiber Length (um)]
      ,[total_fibers] [Total Length of Fibers (mm)]
      ,[result] [Test Result]
FROM [PMDA-Litmus].[dbo].[RecJomesa_SedimentTest]

WHERE [partName] in ($PartName)AND
[loc] in ($Location)
AND DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00')) 
      BETWEEN 
            DATEADD(second, DATEDIFF(second,GETUTCDATE(),Getdate()),$__timeFrom()) 
            AND 
            DATEADD(second, DATEDIFF(second,GETUTCDATE(),Getdate()),$__timeTo()) 
ORDER BY
      DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))

SELECT encode(base64_data,'base64')
FROM "01A"."Base64_Images"
WHERE filename like concat('%',$ReportNum,'%')

SELECT DISTINCT DATEADD(second, CONVERT(bigint, [dateOfAnalysis]) / 1000, CONVERT(datetime, '1-1-1970  05:00:00'))[Date of Analysis]
      ,[reportNum] [Test No.]

      ,[loc] [Sample Location]
      ,[JK] [J-K]
      ,[HI] [H-I]
      ,[FG] [F-G]
      ,[CE] [C-E]
      ,[weight] [Weight (mg)]
      ,[numOfComponents] [Components on Filter]
      ,[partWeight] [Weight Per Part (mg)]
      ,[occ] [Occupancy (%)]
